init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The power of Magic is the only hope for humanity, and will be key to its survival.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She is someone who knows that the power has to be shared between humans and they have to protect it with their lives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But there is a great threat to the world that must be defeated.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They find the time spell in an ancient book and successfully cast it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: While the world is frozen, the aliens decide to leave because they think no one is around.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Now it is up to them to save mana.
